WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.533 --> 00:00:04.100
How dare you!

2
00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:07.800
No parents

3
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.866
No one wants you

4
00:00:12.333 --> 00:00:14.466
I warned you not to hurt him again

5
00:00:14.466 --> 00:00:16.200
Did you turn a deaf ear to what I said?

6
00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:17.333
Ah no

7
00:00:17.333 --> 00:00:20.166
Yes, it was Xia Wanchen who asked me to come

8
00:00:21.166 --> 00:00:23.566
If you want to find him, find him and me

9
00:00:23.733 --> 00:00:24.833
You let me go

10
00:00:24.933 --> 00:00:25.533
Give me a break.

11
00:00:25.533 --> 00:00:26.333
old five

12
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:28.433
Aren't you missing a sparring partner?

13
00:00:29.266 --> 00:00:31.600
Take the grievances that my little sister has suffered over the years

14
00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:33.366
Give it all back to him

15
00:00:34.733 --> 00:00:35.600
Don't worry.

16
00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:38.000
I will definitely keep him from seeing the sun tomorrow

17
00:00:40.366 --> 00:00:43.666
Promise to help me plead with your brothers?

18
00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:45.600
Tell them to let me go this time

19
00:00:45.733 --> 00:00:47.633
If I had known earlier that you were the daughter of the Lu family

20
00:00:47.666 --> 00:00:48.766
Even if you give me ten thousand courage

21
00:00:48.766 --> 00:00:50.200
I wouldn't dare to hurt you either.

22
00:00:51.266 --> 00:00:54.566
I gave you a chance before, but you didn't take it yourself

23
00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:56.933
Now you end up like this

24
00:00:56.933 --> 00:00:59.033
It's what you deserve.

25
00:01:01.666 --> 00:01:03.666
Uh-huh.

26
00:01:05.566 --> 00:01:07.233
Thank you for saving me

27
00:01:07.966 --> 00:01:11.066
Why are fools and brothers so polite?

28
00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:14.066
Now that the matter has been resolved

29
00:01:14.366 --> 00:01:16.100
You don't have to act anymore

